 https://substack.com/redirect/78df946b-9e22-4b9f-b0c2-75685a069bbd?j=3DeyJ=
1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], =E2=80=9CEve=
ry week, amid all the technical meetings on engine and rocket design, he he=
