he imagined what a Mars colony would look like and how it should be governe=
d.=E2=80=9D
Elon=E2=80=99s former Chief of Staff, Sam Teller, recalled a 2014 SpaceX bo=
ard meeting on the same theme: =E2=80=9CThey=E2=80=99re sitting around seri=
ously discussing plans to build a city on Mars and what people will wear th=
ere,=E2=80=9D Teller later marveled, =E2=80=9Cand everyone=E2=80=99s just a=
cting like this is a totally normal conversation.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
On the surface, it seems absurd. In 2014, the Starship rocket that might on=
e day carry humans to the Red Planet was nine years away from its first tes=
