rs away. And the first successful landing of a Falcon 9 first stage, the re=
usability that would make the whole thing possible in the first place, woul=
dn=E2=80=99t happen for another year and a half. But here was the board, sp=
ending precious meeting time debating Martian fashion.=C2=A0
Your first reaction might be that Elon is weird, and he is the boss, and so=
 everyone humors him. His former assistant, Elissa Butterfield, told Isaacs=
on, =E2=80=9CWe tried to avoid ever skipping Mars Colonizer, because that w=
as the most fun meeting for him and put him in a good mood.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
But it wasn=E2=80=99t just Elon.=C2=A0
