9cd483d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU =
], an eleven-year SpaceX veteran, gave up a salary, stock options, and the =
enviable position as a senior jack-of-all-trades engineer at the world=E2=
=80=99s most ambitious company to fix an existential problem he helped unco=
ver, simulated, solved for, and presented to Elon and the team in a Mars Co=
