In a meeting with Tom Mueller [ https://substack.com/redirect/15fe7137-e22a=
-42e8-a9c9-883464b6925d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbq=
Osa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], now the CEO of Impulse Space, and Elon, Doug remembers, =
=E2=80=9CElon said the word nuclear first.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
SpaceX had no nuclear division. Unlike solar, Elon didn=E2=80=99t have a nu=
clear company on the side. The company had no nuclear code, nothing on the =
topic except for a few studies that Mueller, already a big nuclear fan, had=
