Here=E2=80=99s Radiant=E2=80=99s logic. If humanity is to be multiplanetary=
, we need nuclear reactors on Mars. To make nuclear reactors for Mars, you =
need to make a nuclear reactor that works on earth. To make a nuclear react=
or that works on earth, you need money. To make money, you need to mass pro=
duce nuclear reactors on earth and sell power from those nuclear reactors t=
o customers who need it at a price they can afford. To do that, you need ap=
proval to make nuclear reactors. To do that, you need data. To do that, you=
