lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px =
0;"><span>When Doug concluded his study, he had his answer: </span><strong>=
nuclear could achieve SpaceX&#8217;s objectives on Mars</strong><span>. And=
 he had his self-assigned marching orders: </span><strong>&#8220;OK, after =
we build Starship, this is the thing to do and build,&#8221; he said, &#822=
0;This is the mission statement.&#8221;</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Remember, SpaceX people are dead serious about building=
 a civilization on Mars. Elon takes time out of his insane schedule every w=
eek for Mars Colonizer. Doug, realizing that humans would have to farm on M=
ars and that he didn&#8217;t know how to farm, </span><strong>ripped the gr=
ass out of his family&#8217;s front yard and started planting wheat with hi=
s kids to practice.</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><div class=3D"captioned-=
image-container-static" style=3D"font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
