LEU) fuel in damage-resistant TRISO (TRIstructural-ISOtropic) fuel particle=
s, which could be run for several years without refueling and use passive s=
afety systems that can shut down safely on their own.&#160;</p><p style=3D"=
color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;">Project Pele was a loud, clanging siren for Doug. He knew that the Do=
D must have put out the request with a supplier in mind &#8211; the Defense=
 Science Board reviewed many companies three years prior to creating the pr=
ogram to ensure its specs were reasonable and that the RFP would generate s=
ufficient replies &#8211; but he thought that SpaceX should compete anyway.=
&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Nuclear was too important to the plan, an=
d no new reactors had been built in such a long time. Having the DoD behind=
 the project could change that. It could solve all of nuclear&#8217;s chall=
enges &#8211; funding, customer, and regulatory &#8211; within one entity, =
which meant that the time was right for </span><em>some </em><span>company =
to be the company that built a new reactor.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"col=
or: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0=
;"><span>He thought that company should be SpaceX, and tried to set up a nu=
clear team within the friendly confines of the space giant. Meanwhile, sinc=
e the DoD had requested proposals, he went on sabbatical to temporarily go =
full-time on the project, pulling together an informal crack team that incl=
uded Firmware Engineer </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/b260=
b376-7efa-48c9-bcde-ce53e12960df?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZj=
mlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decorat=
ion: underline;">Bob Urberger</a><span>, to submit one. The team came up wi=
th a name &#8211; </span><strong>Radiant </strong><span>&#8211; and a logo,=
 and even set up a legal entity through which they submitted the proposal.<=
/span></p><div class=3D"captioned-image-container-static" style=3D"font-siz=
