n America and the Nuclear Regulatory Commission&#8217;s (NRC) chicken-and-e=
gg approach to regulation.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Back in the first Ato=
mic Age, after the US dropped nuclear bombs on Japan, there was tremendous =
excitement around using that same newfound capability that humans had gaine=
d, the ability to release huge amounts of energy by splitting atoms, for go=
od.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heig=
ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In 1953, President Eisenhower addressed the =
United Nations General Assembly to deliver what would come to be known as t=
he &#8220;Atoms for Peace&#8221; speech.&#160;</p><a href=3D"https://substa=
ck.com/redirect/7ca26cc9-4510-4c3b-aa98-e0c1160206a5?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ=
=2Egb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6=
m8ExkRNpU" target=3D"_blank" class=3D"yo=
utube-wrap" data-component-name=3D"Youtube2ToDOMStatic" style=3D"display: b=
lock; margin: 1.6em 0;"><img src=3D"https://substackcdn.com/image/youtube/w=
_550,c_limit/l_youtube_play_qyqt8q,w_120/oxGSfOd1Dpc" style=3D"-ms-interpol=
ation-mode: bicubic; border: none !important; display: block; height: auto;=
 margin: 0 auto; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;"></a=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;">President Eisenhower imagined that, &#8220;if the entire=
 body of the world's scientists and engineers had adequate amounts of fissi=
onable material with which to test and develop their ideas, this capability=
 would rapidly be transformed into universal, efficient, and economic usage=
=2E&#8221;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54,=
 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>They did, and it was. On </span><em><a =
href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/d5b34299-d66c-4361-a8ee-2b9b61b70d8b?=
j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">Age of Miracles<=
/a></em><span>, nuclear engineer and author of the excellent </span><a href=
=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/5153d753-3962-4912-8f32-b0c4f8161a27?j=3D=
eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">whatisnuclear.com<=
/a><span> </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/7b9a5137-eec6-458=
a-bb90-be14cfba7659?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8=
-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underlin=
e;">Nick Touran</a><span> told me and </span><a href=3D"https://substack.co=
m/redirect/2090649d-5c87-4133-bb58-0a23c117528b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J=
5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55=
); text-decoration: underline;">Julia DeWahl</a><span> that the period was =
a time of incredible experimentation in nuclear power:&#160;</span></p><blo=
ckquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #0c2427; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0=
;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; =
margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><span>There was a time back in =
the 40s, 50s, 60s, where there were a hundred thousand people around the wo=
rld, the smartest people in the world, all focused on nuclear reactor techn=
ology. It was like The Thing. And so there's so much interesting informatio=
n and history and things that people did back then. It just blows my mind. =
Every time I go, look, I find something new. </span><strong>We had lots of =
