oving that a particular reactor design is safe, but it won&#8217;t allow co=
mpanies to test their reactors in order to generate that data!</strong><spa=
n> That&#8217;s so maddening to even type that it&#8217;s a small miracle a=
ny entrepreneur is willing to build a nuclear startup.&#160;</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><span>But entrepreneurs are clever and resilient, and many ar=
