pan><strong>And one path around the roadblocks is to test a reactor in one =
of the DOE&#8217;s national labs, like, for example, Idaho National Lab.</s=
trong><span>&#160;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Contra the NRC, =
the DOE is awesome. It&#8217;s quite literally the good half of the AEC. I =
