olar EROEI is lower, it&#8217;s clear that </span><strong>the challenge for=
 nuclear isn&#8217;t one of physics. It&#8217;s one of our ability to build=
=2E</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p=20=
style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>This is the same p=
oint made by guests on </span><em>Age of Miracles,</em><span> like Valar At=
