e power company might have to install power lines at $1 million per mile ju=
st to get you going. In this hypothetical future, you&#8217;d be off the gr=
id, operating wherever you want, whenever you want.&#160;</p><p style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px =
0;"><span>All of the technology exists to make this happen. Most of it has =
